<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2046" TARGET=_self>DUDE...get a freagin bow.</A> (Gray Rage (DB))
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>sup all

<BR>i play a barbarian warrior, and learining archery was my first concern for fights....wizards always root, hehe, cause they die if they don't....
<P>usualy its fun when u resist his first root, because the guy knows he screwed when u resisted that....secondly, even if he roots u (i have bad luck sometimes in resisting the stuipid thing) USE A BOW, it will rip him piece by piece, plus u'll prob disrrupt some of his killer spells, not to mention put holes in his pretty robes....
<P>there are alotta bows that do big dmg, but u might wanna take those with awsome delay, since your goal mostly is to disrupt him, and the dmg is included since u probably have double attack...hey, u might not like it, maybe it isnt fast enough, maybe the dmg isnt too big, but if u think about it, its better then watching the wizzie blast u with his powerful spells
<P>i still think wizards are a bit more powerful, and i would be stuipid if i didnt say this...i just hope eq puts some more good bows into the game, and perhaps a few magic items that raise the magic resistance...
<P>well, thats my advice to ya peeps
<BR>good luck in fighting those spellcasters, if u try, u'll hardly lose
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
